u\'ve had any recent tests done outside of the hospital, please bring the reports with you, if available. Please bring your RAMQ card as well as your blue Opal General Hospital card.<br/><b><br/>What should I expect during this appointment? </b><br/><br/>You should expect to meet with Dr. Metrakos and discuss about your current symptoms, your physical health and more. This information will be used to help him better care for you and your needs. Feel free to write down any questions you may have and bring them with you to the follow-up appointment.</p>', NULL, 20, 2, '#D50000', 1, '2022-01-21 17:58:01', 13, '2018-11-07 16:06:13', 'gKeATBcIa8'),
