odeau).</li><li>De donner votre consentement verbal pour participer à une consultation téléphonique ou en vidéo avec K. Thibodeau.</li></ul><p><b>Que dois-je apporter à ce rendez-vous ?</b><br/>Veuillez avoir une liste de vos médicaments, y compris les médicaments en ventre libre.<br/><br/><b>&#144;À quoi devrais-je m\'attendre lors de ce rendez-vous ?</b><br/>Vous devriez vous attendre à rencontrer K. Thibodeau pour discuter de vos difficultés et besoins psychosociaux actuels, de votre santé physique et de bien d\'autres choses encore. Ces informations seront utilisées par votre thérapeute pour vous fournir les soins appropriés.<br/></p>', '<p><b>General Information</b><br/>Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, onsite visits to MUHC hospital clinics have been reduced or, in some cases, stopped. Instead of coming to the hospital for your visit, your nurse, doctor or other health care professional will use the telephone or the computer to perform video consultations to complement your care and to make sure that good communication continues between you and your health care team.   <br/><br/><b>What is the purpose of this appointment?</b><br/>This is a follow-up appointment with your couple and family therapist K. Thibodeau, done by phone or videoconference. During this appointment, K. Thibodeau will assess your psychosocial condition and may discuss any of the following issues with you:</p><p></p><ul><li>Review your psychological history </li><li>Review the result of the distress screening tools</li></ul><p><br/><b>Who will I meet at this appointment?</b><br/>You will speak with K. Thibodeau.<br/><br/><b>Where will this appointment take place?</b><br/>This appointment will take place at in the location of your choice, usually in your home. It is advised that you choose an environment that maintains your privacy and confidentiality during this medical consultation.<br/><br/><b>How should I prepare for this appointment?</b><br/>Since you will be using your telephone, computer o